<h2>
<a href="https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/north-korean-military-threatens-to-re-enter-demilitarised-areas/article31839859.ece" class="s4x-100-ls-heading" title="Updated: June 16, 2020 12:22 IST&#013;Published: June 16, 2020 12:22 IST">
North Korean military threatens to re-enter demilitarised areas </a>
</h2>
<a href='#' class='person-name no-lnk'>AP</a>
<p class="s4-3x100-text s4x-100-ls-text hidden-xs hidden-sm hidden-md">
